text:
Vehicle and Traffic Amendment (Offensive Advertising) Act 2017 (Repealed)

1. (Repealed)
    The Vehicle and Traffic Amendment (Offensive Advertising) Act 2017 has been repealed by section 14 of the Vehicle and Traffic Amendment (Offensive Advertising) Act 2017
